        <ontology:hasDescription>The type of innovation of this VC (Value Chain) is Endogenous and Exogenous. Different innovative initiatives have arisen related to: the traceability control system thanks to the development of computer applications; creation of species identification centers; development of a program of socio-cultural activities, exhibitions, etc.; processing and buying and selling companies; the &amp;apos;Montes de Soria&amp;apos; association as an instrument of use, management and governance; development of mycotourism activities; synergies with the rural tourism and hospitality sector; development of second homes in the municipality. The innovation is related to New products, New processes, New marketing strategies and New governance systems. The land use systems involved are Forestry. The local assets include Natural, social and cultural.  </ontology:hasDescription>
    </NamedIndividual>
    


